TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);
$soln = "$a";

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Determine whether the integral is divergent or convergent.
If it is convergent, evaluate it. If not, state your answer as "divergent."
$BR \[ \int_{0}^{\infty} $a e^{-x} dx \]
$BR $BR \{ans_rule( 30) \}
$BR
EOT

ANS(num_cmp($soln));

